    • Constructor Detail

      • ScriptRef

        public ScriptRef(java.lang.String name)
        Creates a script reference with the given name. Adding this to a major record's ScriptPackage will attach the script to the record. Of course, there must be a script with that name in the Data/Scripts/ folder for it to actually do anything in-game.
        Parameters:
        name -
